# 📝 Todo List App

A simple and responsive Todo List application that helps users organize daily tasks efficiently. Users can create, update, complete, and delete tasks with an intuitive interface.

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add new tasks
- ✏️ Edit existing tasks
- ✔️ Mark tasks as completed
- 🗑️ Delete tasks
- 🔍 Filter tasks (All, Active, Completed)
- 💾 Persistent storage (Local Storage / Database)
- 📱 Responsive design

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)

**Optional**
- React / Vue / Angular
- Tailwind CSS / Bootstrap
- Node.js & Express
- MongoDB / Firebase

## 📂 Project Structure

```
todo-list/
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── script.js
│── assets/
│── README.md
```

## ⚙️ Installation

1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/todo-list.git
```

2. Navigate to the project

```bash
cd todo-list
```

3. Open the project

- Open `index.html` in your browser

Or, if using Node.js:

```bash
npm install
npm start
```

